      • ATM

        protected ATM(double money,
              double fee,
              boolean loadHistoricalRecords,
              boolean startConsole)
        Initialize the availableAmountInMachine, transactionFee and all other fields. And then start this application. It is a protected constructor because careless use may wipe the whole transaction data.
        Parameters:
        money: - The available amount of money this machine has.
        fee: - Some fee will be charged on every transaction.
        loadHistoricalRecords: - True to load history account records. False if you do not want to.
